9-08-15T00:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個訪問好清晰～呀姐講得好好！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=718312668603001&amp;id=680087995758802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D718312668603001%26id%3D680087995758802&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=da2b7e7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=718312668603001&amp;id=680087995758802</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:16:13.000Z","msg":"啲狗無智商又無情商<br />\n最慘bb 仔，唔舒服只係識喊，講唔到人知邊度唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家住內街的劉先生目擊警方，向內街的食店門外發射2枚催淚彈，趕走很多食宵夜的街坊，「X你老母黐線嘅九唔搭八，（街坊）食緊飯，仲喺度放催淚彈，係咪儍架班警察？」、「你要癲就喺出面癲，唔好喺度癲啦&hellip;&hellip;（示威者）有冇行入嚟，都唔好喺度（放煙），呢度成條街都係食肆」、「X你老母放埋炸彈吖笨X！」麥先生駕車來買宵夜，警方即射催淚彈過來，但「放完就即刻走啦喎，佢唔係嚟驅趕人喎。」<br />\n<br />\n有身穿工作制服的女士途經現場，吸入催淚煙不適，難以開口說話。有夜歸的女街坊以毛巾掩面，被問為何不戴口罩時，拋下一句：「戴咗（警察）就話你係暴徒、又話拉嘞，佢連買支筆都拉。」有吸入催淚煙不適的男子更坐在港鐵站出口，由救護員治理。有小食店的食物被催淚煙污染要即棄，至少損失過千元；住在附近的老闆慨嘆，得知警方會放催淚煙，已趕過來收舖，但仍來不及收起食物。"},{"pid":"b5fa4b29f7b319144907eae2086dbe7bf49dc803","tid":1473432,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"中途個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a645065874db4cc4feda4a149a763b5fed6d1a9","tid":1473432,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:10.000Z","msg":"推 721 811"},{"pid":"91dabe3dd85d4e697ff01c2bb201d5b02438f449","tid":1473432,"uid":285318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"其實深水埗嗰邊商戶系咪可以去小額審裁處告克警亂射催淚彈? 濃煙湧入鋪頭/餐廳，員工/顧客/食客擔心有害物質殘留店內，損害健康，打擊生意<br />\n<br />\n克警影響商戶當日及近期生意，商戶係咪有權拎返相應賠償?<br />\n<br />\n附近居民需自費檢查身體受有害氣體影響嘅程度同健康狀況，樓上居民係咪有權拎返相應賠償?"}]}